<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">هـ ذ ر م:</span> <span class="c2">(الْهَذْرَمَةُ)</span> السُّرْعَةُ فِي الْقِرَاءَةِ وَالْكَلَامِ يُقَالُ: <span class="c2">(هَذْرَمَ)</span> وِرْدَهُ أَيْ هَذَّهُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>